{
  "stem": "23090.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The barrack consisted of like, horse windows.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was a, a wooden floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one end of the barrack was like, a 55-gallon drum, a cut 55-gallon drum.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this is where you had to go to relieve yourself, if you had to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, needless to tell you, that dysentery, sickness, disease, which we-- was already there prior to our coming.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were comparatively healthy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So if you were a healthy person coming in there, other than hungry, you are, you are thrown into a, a infested, disease infested, condition.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That doesn't take very long to succumb to that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the, the thing that I'll never forget to this day is when I, I, I was given some of the food or some of the-- it was water soup and-- with some potato peelings.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I contracted dysentery, diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I needed to make it to the, to this drum.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That's the only way you can go is somehow find a position so you can sit on this drum, so you can go, so you can relieve yourself.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And while you were going there, from one end to the barrack to the other, most of the people couldn't make it to this place.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So they obviously just relieved themselves on this way, on this wooden plank, on this wooden floor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then when you were trying to get back to your, to your bunk, to your place, you were covered with all this, and you had nothing to wipe yourself with.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See, in Auschwitz, you were allowed to go to the bathroom in unison, and, and, and-- a certain time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not when you needed to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's when they delegated for you to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
